description:
The Olympics! It’s one of the world’s biggest events, drawing scores of nations together, focusing billions of eyes on exceptional athletes. Entire nations find themselves caught up in the drama of victory and defeat. That's when Jesse Owens shined. Watch our new program, "Gold Medal Hero: Jesse Owens" and discover how God can turn unfavourable circumstances to your advantage.
